<div class="row project">
		<div class="twelvecol">
			
			<h3>TV Reinvented</h3>
			<p class="metadata">2012 &middot; self initiated &middot; TV</p>
			<p>A self-initiated design project inspired by the television and second-screen experiences I&rsquo;ve had the pleasure of working on. My proposal integrates broadcast and streaming content into a 10-foot UI that is quickly navigated with a directional pad on a super simple remote control. Programming is curated in a <em>My Media</em> screen when logged into one&rsquo;s personal user profile, all displayed on the backdrop of stunning artwork.</p>
		</div>
	</div>	
	<div class="row project">
		<div class="twelvecol">
			
			<h3>Mobile Before It Was Cool</h3>
			<p class="metadata">2010 &middot; Oakley &middot; web &middot; mobile</p>
			<p>In 2010, Oakley.com was seeing an increasing number of visitors from mobile devices. Seeing an opportunity to increase conversion, I designed a mobile website that makes it easy to find and purchase products. Being the sole designer on this project, I completed research, interaction design, and UI design for Oakley/Luxottica&rsquo;s first mobile initiative.</p>
